

URL = http:// www.myhomelife.org.uk

=Description=

"The timing was perfect for a national movement of people involved with care homes for older people, and My Home Life have filled that gap. They work together to improve the quality of life of people living, dying, visiting and working in care homes. The website provides a wealth of open content: from research reports to forums and a video series on the evidence of best practice in care homes. They also run leadership support and community development programmes with care home staff, helping to foster positive changes and relationship-centred care in care homes."
